snippet.title: Stirring Abyss - Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Brave the depths in Stirring Abyss, an upcoming tactical RPG combining deep sea exploration and strategy. Lead a secret U.S. Navy expedition during the height of the Cold War and help your crew uncover ancient mysteries and escape the abyss!

https://stirringabyss.com
https://www.facebook.com/sleepysentry/
https://twitter.com/SleepySentry

Music and Sound Effects by Red Forge
https://redforge.bandcamp.com/
https://twitter.com/redforgemusic

Voice Over by May Charters
http://www.maycharters.com/
